Name: IC
Variable description: Informed consent was administered to participant
Scoring: 1 = IC was administered, 0 = IC was not administered

Name: FD
Variable description: Participant was provided a funelled debriefing
Scoring: 1 = FD was administered, 0 = FD was not administered

Name: Comp.
Scoring: 1 = compensation (0.5 SONA credit & Amazon album) was delivered, 0 = compensation was not delivered

Name: Album.sent
Variable description: Date participant's selected album was emailed via downloadable Amazon MP3 file

Name: AC
Scoring: The album the participant selected when presented with a choice between the 5th and 6th ranked albums from their initial ranking form

Name: ACIR
Variable description: Rank participant gave to their selected album on the initial ranking form

Name: ACSR
Variable description: Rank participant gave to their selected album on the secondary ranking form

Name: N/O
Variable description: Number of albums owned out of the 30 listed albums
Scoring: Total determined by the number of albums crossed out on the album selection form

Name: BeforeDV
Variable description: Before the treatment: The difference between the Rank of Chosen and Rank of Rejected (Rank of Chosen - Rank of Rejected)

Name: AfterDV
Variable description: After the treatment: The difference between the Rank of Chosen and Rank of Rejected (Rank of Chosen - Rank of Rejected)

Name: Difference
Variable full label: Difference between ranks before and after
